Data License

The datasets ingested and processed by this software are obtained from third-
party open data portals (Ajuntament de València and Generalitat Valenciana)
and retain their original licenses. The historical dataset of air quality
measurements from the Portal de Dades Obertes de l'Ajuntament de València
is distributed under Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC-BY-4.0).

When redistributing data derived from these sources, please maintain
attribution to the original data providers:

- Red de Vigilancia y Control de Contaminación Atmosférica (RVVCCA)
- Ajuntament de València — Portal de Dades Obertes
- Generalitat Valenciana — Conselleria de Medi Ambient
